[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/comments/502459615","html_url":"https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/798#issuecomment-502459615","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/798","id":502459615,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUwMjQ1OTYxNQ==","user":{"login":"karip","id":6185066,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYxODUwNjY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6185066?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip","html_url":"https://github.com/karip","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-06-16T14:57:03Z","updated_at":"2019-06-16T14:57:03Z","body":"I think I have found the reason for this issue. The [BaseStrokeContent.java](https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android/blob/master/lottie/src/main/java/com/airbnb/lottie/animation/content/BaseStrokeContent.java) multiplies dash pattern values by parentMatrix scale, but it doesn't multiply the dash offset value.\r\n\r\nChanging [these lines](https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android/blob/47fc0dc23d9088bd3c9c0174a86e1a8edb3c0beb/lottie/src/main/java/com/airbnb/lottie/animation/content/BaseStrokeContent.java#L299):\r\n\r\n    float offset = dashPatternOffsetAnimation == null ? 0f : dashPatternOffsetAnimation.getValue();\r\n    paint.setPathEffect(new DashPathEffect(dashPatternValues, offset));\r\n    L.endSection(\"StrokeContent#applyDashPattern\");\r\n\r\nto multiply offset by scale fixes the issue:\r\n\r\n    float offset = dashPatternOffsetAnimation == null ? 0f : dashPatternOffsetAnimation.getValue();\r\n    offset *= scale;\r\n    paint.setPathEffect(new DashPathEffect(dashPatternValues, offset));\r\n    L.endSection(\"StrokeContent#applyDashPattern\");\r\n\r\nI'm not sure what is parentMatrix (global document matrix?), but this change seems to fix the issue.\r\n\r\nCan you make this one line fix or do you want me to create a pull request?\r\n\r\nI tested this code with the JSON file I had attached above. I also tested it with few other documents created with Keyshape (it's a Mac app with a Lottie exporter). Unfortunately, I don't currently have access to After Effects, so I couldn't test it with animations created in it. It would be great if this fix was tested with path offset animations created in After Effects to verify that the issue is really fixed.\r\n","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/airbnb/lottie-android/issues/comments/502459615/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"karip","id":6185066,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYxODUwNjY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6185066?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip","html_url":"https://github.com/karip","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karip/repos","events_url":"https://api.gi